## Integration Test Requirements

### Lab Runtime Tests
```rust
/// Test: Same seed produces same message ordering
#[test]
fn test_deterministic_scheduling() {
    let trace1 = run_with_seed(42);
    let trace2 = run_with_seed(42);
    assert_eq\!(trace1, trace2);
}

/// Test: ActorLeakOracle detects orphaned actors
#[test]
